Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.70,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.76,0:00:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.03,0:00:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.74,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾儿放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.88,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.94,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.68,0:01:03.88,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.95,0:01:10.88,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.96,0:01:15.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.57,0:01:24.87,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.48,0:01:39.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.92,0:01:47.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.20,0:01:54.23,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.30,0:02:05.18,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.76,0:02:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}步步逼近\NPositional play
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,货物就是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.13,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送货的，辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作结束了，快回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾儿…放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.62,0:03:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是另一半酬劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亚力克斯．罗威吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去装货了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛温
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别对货物太粗鲁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还赶得上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊\N你就算用填充剂作应急处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有燃料还是飞不起来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料我现在就去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着慢着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难不成要用那家伙的燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人已经…死了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，还是算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了艾儿\N总共已经死了三个人了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到\N亚力克斯他的眼神了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种人居然也能在天上飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他的眼神可不是那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.55,0:07:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，任务已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经把货送到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务就到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没问清楚\N他们打算怎么处理艾儿之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务还不算结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,货物如果没有安全送达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务就等于失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好幼稚哦，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…忘了把这带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们帮她送去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿她应该需要这个的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险度恐怕可以到十颗星呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇你也满幼稚的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪比得上克劳士你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这燃料是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浓度高得一塌糊涂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不调整混合比例的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小家伙的引擎会烧坏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然可以用这么厉害的燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会是…基尔特公会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.93,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为就那样丢掉\N未免太可惜了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说可以拿来维修先锋艇呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你这个性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存钱可是很重要的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面\N艾儿薇丝．汉弥尔敦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫苏菲亚\N是这艘船的副舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想必累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证你可以在这里\N过得很舒适的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么需要别客气尽管说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以为你做些什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿我会送吃的过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要当个保姆\N恐怕你的笑容还嫌不够哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜你在偷看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会做那么不识趣的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是直觉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过真想不到副舰长\N你居然会亲自来照顾小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要换你来做做看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜．魏斯洛跟您报到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,货物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.81,0:10:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魏斯洛，你到皇帝那里跑一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他货物已经安全送到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后桅杆观测台传来报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七点钟方向有一架\N来路不明的先锋艇正在接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料不够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算纯度再怎么高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照你这种飙法\N顶多也只够单程用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.92,0:11:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.19,0:11:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，给我逮到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是发光信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…它说不准靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用理它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…还是得回它一句话才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一句话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，好歹这也是工作嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,礼貌上应该要打声招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰要对我们开炮了\N你究竟打了什么招呼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只说了\N我们送东西过来而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被那种东西打中了\N保证一命呜呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲上去，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要上了船\N他们就拿我们没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么真的开炮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要从后面绕过去，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.99,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.96,0:13:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见吧，我短暂的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.31,0:13:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的对空炮火是在玩假的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那架先锋艇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魏斯洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它真像以前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这就和艾丽丝蒂亚\N一起出发到皇帝那边去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天你还挺健谈的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.88,0:14:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高度没办法拉高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料也到了极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是坠落还是击落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是死路一条啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，不可以放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我紧急迫降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定先锋艇已打开空气煞车器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我居然还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的小羊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接…接得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把钩子找个地方钩起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.07,0:15:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，到这边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有升降机\N说不定可以利用它到上面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说他们为什么要停止射击啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚明明就是\N击落我们的好机会说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他们根本就\N没把我们看在眼里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方那么大\N真的找得到艾儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只希望他们\N不要突然朝我们开枪才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像停机库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.61,0:15:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法再往上了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.89,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.03,0:16:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是曾经救过我们的那架先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.01,0:16:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不满意刚才的另一半酬劳吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.49,0:16:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的强行登舰\N我还是头一次看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说不满意我们也一样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.87,0:16:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看银之战舰都被你们\N用那架破铜烂铁给刮伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.71,0:16:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破铜烂铁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.27,0:17:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至于伤到银之战舰的人\N会有什么下场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我来告诉你们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了任务而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.12,0:17:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到这里来\N总不会是为了送这布娃娃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是有人托我要交给艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是被你们带到这里来的\N那个小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委托人就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是送货员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成了任务我立刻就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我挺中意这小子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经在给他打分数啦\N盖尔老爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你是不知道\N什么叫有勇无谋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.69,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀，那就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西就交给我吧，送货员…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西要直接交给本人\N这是规矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.24,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是拜托人应该有的态度吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来不让你吃点苦头\N你是不会明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙啊，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你最好别惹他们生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得那传闻吗，肯定是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.76,0:18:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.79,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.73,0:18:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫我让开耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.47,0:18:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子口气挺跩的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像还没弄清楚\N这里是哪里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.51,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀，寇斯塔比下手还真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我来把垃圾给扔了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.06,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.93,0:18:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.96,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向队长敬礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长在问你话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.85,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫克劳士．沃卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会记住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操作器检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.57,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仪表与计时器检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料活栓保持开启
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混合剂充足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出动前检查项目全部完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.02,0:20:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们要找那个小孩\N可以到舰桥上问问看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要人家报名字\N你自己的就不说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你在跟谁说话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜．魏斯洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会记住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.59,0:21:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魏斯洛队长\N可是很少会问人家名字的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.96,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥一定就在这上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.76,0:21:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不是走错地方了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿她在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.25,0:22:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有东西要交给艾儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.85,0:22:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.75,0:22:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士你振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.22,0:22:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.66,0:22:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.21,0:22:40.37,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.12,0:22:58.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.26,0:23:03.79,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.87,0:23:12.57,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.65,0:23:18.52,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.58,0:23:24.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.39,0:23:30.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.26,0:23:35.96,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.04,0:23:48.00,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.46,0:23:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回预告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.12,0:23:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿你在这儿，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.66,0:23:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问克劳士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.49,0:23:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士他就在你面前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.10,0:24:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，艾儿说你好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.90,0:24:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你那张肿得三倍大的脸\N可不可以处理一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.40,0:24:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要我怎么办嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.21,0:24:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最后流亡 第六话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.95,0:24:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,审判者的攻击\NArbiter attack
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.21,0:24:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.35,0:24:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦\N你是要我帮你说对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.48,0:24:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位观众，下周也敬请期待啰
